net.i2p.router.news

Class NewsXMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.i2p.router.news.NewsXMLParser

  • public class NewsXMLParser
extends Object
    Parse out the news.xml file which is in Atom format (RFC4287). We use the XML parser from the UPnP library.
    Since:
    0.9.17
